text: Jiří Pecháček (born 5 August 1943) is a Czech equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Czechoslovakia Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Plzeň-North District
